{"tid":2239690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣將會有德國制既武漢肺炎疫苗","createTime":"2020-10-12T06:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d44eb7a2e1e728a26b490e4348b49e46e5ca46b","tid":2239690,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"東洋 (4105-TW) 今 (12) 日宣布，取得德國 BioNTech 新冠肺炎疫苗的台灣代理權，預計下午召開記者會，由董事長林全親自出面說明。 東洋表示，過去一直有與 BioNTech 聯繫，今日才正式簽約，此外，目前全球進入臨床三期試驗的疫苗不多，其中進度最快、最有機會通過審核的就是德國 BNT 研製的疫苗，而台灣東洋正式在今日取得在台代理授權。 東洋指出，BNT 授權台灣東洋藥品最多 3000 萬劑新冠疫苗，後續將與台灣主管機關協商，並由林全親自出面說明 BNT 疫苗研製進展，以及冷鏈、倉儲等因應配套作為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4532604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4532604&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=86454353\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4532604</a>"},{"pid":"8de9e5def1e454ab8b82852a881828ef709a9ec6","tid":2239690,"uid":141668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"三民主義 吾黨所宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nEinigkeit und Recht und Freiheit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a01134b5a9375200ebc7c5a755d02bde5f4d8d","tid":2239690,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"601a1d5bbce1ecb421c1aca83976108344513240","tid":2239690,"uid":92125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"我要做台灣人呀 屌你"},{"pid":"3e686f6e2edb176896bee318b17d257f086b09f4","tid":2239690,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"製"}]}